# {{ .ProjectName }}

Built with [Dokrypt](https://dokrypt.com) — Docker for Web3.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Start local blockchain
dokrypt up

# Deploy contracts
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network localhost

# Run tests
forge test
```

## Contracts

- **Counter.sol** — Simple counter with increment/decrement
- **SimpleToken.sol** — Minimal ERC-20 token with mint

## Commands

```bash
dokrypt up          # Start environment
dokrypt down        # Stop environment
dokrypt status      # Check status
dokrypt accounts    # List accounts
dokrypt logs        # View logs
```
